0e4b			; 
0e4b			; Get a word (16 bit) in hexadecimal notation. The result is returned in HL. 
0e4b			; Since the routines get_byte and therefore get_nibble are called, only valid 
0e4b			; characters (0-9a-f) are accepted. 
